thread.title: BRIEF-Cube.ITG Preliminary FY Net Loss At About 179 Mln Zlotys

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Cube.ITG Preliminary FY Net Loss At About 179 Mln Zlotys
text:
April 25 (Reuters) - CUBE.ITG SA:
* REPORTED ON TUESDAY PRELIMINARY FY NET LOSS OF ABOUT 179 MILLION ZLOTYS
* PRELIM. FY OPERATING LOSS OF ABOUT 163 MILLION ZLOTYS * FY FINANCIAL RESULTS AFFECTED AMONG OTHERS BY REVALUATION WRITE-OFFS AND INTEREST ACCRUED TO COMPANY ON LIABILITIES IN THE AMOUNT OF ABOUT 4 MILLION ZLOTYS
* COURT IN WROCLAW OPENED REHABILITATION PROCEEDINGS FOR CO ON OCT. 18, 2017
